Agris yettmag-d deg yal ideg (amkan) anda llant waman d [[asemmiṭ|usemmiṭ]] s akin ad uɣalen waman s tefrer ar wegris, mi ara ad yuget usemmiṭ (s waṭas n tseddarin ddaw n 0 C°) yezmer ad yennulfu [[adrar|wedrar]] neɣ [[asif|wasif]] n wegris yerna deg waṭas n wakuden llan [[agelmim|igelmimen]] [[agurres|yettgurusen]] s usrag n usemmiṭ yugten maca anagar tissi-ynes tafellayt iy tt-gurrusen ma adis-is yettɣamay d [[amazzal]] <br/>
Azal n ¾ n [[aman iẓidanen|waman iẓidanen]] yellan deg [[tagnit|tegnit]] mmugen deg telɣa n wegris yettilin s wuden agejdan deg [[Antraktika]] d [[Greenland]] d [[tizgelt n ugafa]] d tiqucac n idurar.

